1
00:00:07,006 --> 00:00:09,008
(Koharu) Mr. Kurosaki➡

2
00:00:09,008 --> 00:00:11,511
I've become someone you care about.

3
00:00:11,511 --> 00:00:13,012
(Kurosaki) Huh...?

4
00:00:13,012 --> 00:00:15,014
Is it okay to propose again?

5
00:00:15,014 --> 00:00:17,517
(Kiriya) Wait, wait, wait, wait! Is there a big project underway?

6
00:00:17,517 --> 00:00:20,520
Special appearance? Is it Kurosaki?

7
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:23,520
Request from Mr. Arisugawa.

8
00:00:26,526 --> 00:00:29,028
(Arisugawa) CURO!

9
00:00:29,028 --> 00:00:32,031
I wanted to meet you for the first time in a while!

10
00:00:32,031 --> 00:00:34,033
It's been a long time.

11
00:00:34,033 --> 00:00:36,536
《What... what? 》

12
00:00:36,536 --> 00:00:40,540
"picture? Eh~⁉》

13
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:42,542
This is the delivery of the product. (Customer) Thank you.

14
00:00:42,542 --> 00:00:44,544
thank you very much.

15
00:00:44,544 --> 00:00:46,546
We look forward to seeing you again.

16
00:00:46,546 --> 00:00:49,048
《Who was that person? 》

17
00:00:49,048 --> 00:00:52,552
《A staff member? Or a co-star? 》

18
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:55,054
《Maybe I know you...? 》

19
00:00:55,054 --> 00:00:58,558
《You seemed to get along really well with Kurosaki-san》

20
00:00:58,558 --> 00:01:00,560
《He had his arms crossed...》

21
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:04,998
《No, no, calm down, it can't be helped even if I think about it》

22
00:01:04,998 --> 00:01:08,001
《But... Ah! I'll definitely think about it! 》

23
00:01:08,001 --> 00:01:10,003
(Yui) Koharu-chan!

24
00:01:10,003 --> 00:01:12,505
picture? Ah... welcome!

25
00:01:12,505 --> 00:01:14,507
(Fujita) Hello. Ah, uh...｡

26
00:01:14,507 --> 00:01:17,510
280…｡ (Yao) 3 for 560 yen.

27
00:01:17,510 --> 00:01:19,012
(Fujita) Please.

28
00:01:19,012 --> 00:01:22,015
This rice ball uses mixed grain rice➡

29
00:01:22,015 --> 00:01:24,017
It's good for both beauty and health.

30
00:01:24,017 --> 00:01:27,520
Is that so? Eh, I'm happy and looking forward to today.

31
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:30,523
(Yui) Yeah! I love Shirase rice balls!

32
00:01:30,523 --> 00:01:32,525
Hey, I'm so happy.

33
00:01:32,525 --> 00:01:36,525
Hey, Koharu-chan. Ah, yes.

34
00:01:38,031 --> 00:01:40,533
Yui-chan, please be careful when you return home.

35
00:01:40,533 --> 00:01:42,535
(Yui) Yeah, bye-bye, Yuio-kun!

36
00:01:42,535 --> 00:01:44,537
Bye bye. (Fujita) Thank you very much.

37
00:01:44,537 --> 00:01:46,539
(Yao: Koharu) Thank you very much.

38
00:01:46,539 --> 00:01:48,039
(Fujita) Good.

39
00:01:49,542 --> 00:01:51,544
One week after starting part-time job➡

40
00:01:51,544 --> 00:01:53,546
I can’t believe I’ve already captured the hearts of our regular customers ➡

41
00:01:53,546 --> 00:01:55,548
Yuio-san is amazing.

42
00:01:55,548 --> 00:01:57,550
yes?

43
00:01:57,550 --> 00:02:02,050
I would be very happy if I could be of help to Koharu-chan.

44
00:02:03,490 --> 00:02:05,990
So dazzling...

45
00:02:08,495 --> 00:02:10,997
By the way... are you worried about something?

46
00:02:10,997 --> 00:02:12,499
picture?

47
00:02:12,499 --> 00:02:16,503
Look, I was sighing a lot earlier.

48
00:02:16,503 --> 00:02:19,506
Ah... no, that's...

49
00:02:19,506 --> 00:02:23,510
Maybe... love troubles?

50
00:02:23,510 --> 00:02:26,012
No, that's not it.

51
00:02:26,012 --> 00:02:28,014
Koharu-chan, it's too easy to understand.

52
00:02:28,014 --> 00:02:31,514
No, that's not true! Please don't make fun of me.

53
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:36,022
It's Koharu-chan➡

54
00:02:36,022 --> 00:02:40,026
Aren't you the type of person who can't talk about your worries too much?

55
00:02:40,026 --> 00:02:42,028
yeah….

56
00:02:42,028 --> 00:02:46,533
If you don't mind me, I'll listen to you anytime?

57
00:02:46,533 --> 00:02:50,537
Thank you, Yuo-san.

58
00:02:50,537 --> 00:02:56,042
Phone) (ringtone)

59
00:02:56,042 --> 00:02:59,045
Yes, this is the rice ball shop Shirase.

60
00:02:59,045 --> 00:03:01,045
Ah, Kiriya-san.

61
00:03:02,048 --> 00:03:03,983
Huh?

62
00:03:03,983 --> 00:03:24,003
♬～

63
00:03:24,003 --> 00:03:44,023
♬～

64
00:03:44,023 --> 00:04:00,039
♬～

65
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:04,978
♬～

66
00:04:04,978 --> 00:04:06,478
(Kiriya) Good morning.

67
00:04:14,988 --> 00:04:17,490
He's an amazing person...

68
00:04:17,490 --> 00:04:21,995
That's what makes this movie so powerful.

69
00:04:21,995 --> 00:04:25,999
Thankfully, even though it's only one scene➡

70
00:04:25,999 --> 00:04:29,002
Is it really okay for me to appear in a movie like this?

71
00:04:29,002 --> 00:04:32,005
I'm sure the fans will be happy too.

72
00:04:32,005 --> 00:04:35,008
I hope so...

73
00:04:35,008 --> 00:04:36,509
(Arisugawa) CURO!

74
00:04:36,509 --> 00:04:38,011
Ah... Mr. Arisugawa.

75
00:04:38,011 --> 00:04:42,015
I'm looking forward to shooting it because I'm really excited about it.

76
00:04:42,015 --> 00:04:45,018
We will do our best to avoid any inconvenience.

77
00:04:45,018 --> 00:04:48,021
Hehe what? Are you nervous?

78
00:04:48,021 --> 00:04:51,024
It's my first time acting.

79
00:04:51,024 --> 00:04:55,028
Since I'm here, let's get along fine.

80
00:04:55,028 --> 00:04:56,528
yes.

81
00:04:57,530 --> 00:05:01,534
Kurosaki: I have to change clothes, so could you please go to the waiting room first?

82
00:05:01,534 --> 00:05:02,969
yes.

83
00:05:02,969 --> 00:05:05,471
Ah, if Kiriya-san and Koharu-san come...

84
00:05:05,471 --> 00:05:07,471
Isn't it okay if you wait?

85
00:05:08,975 --> 00:05:10,975
thank you.

86
00:05:17,483 --> 00:05:19,986
I wanted to talk to CURO a little more.

87
00:05:19,986 --> 00:05:21,988
Ah... I'm sorry.

88
00:05:21,988 --> 00:05:24,490
He's not good at interacting with people.

89
00:05:24,490 --> 00:05:26,492
Ah, that's right.

90
00:05:26,492 --> 00:05:28,995
And what about Koharu?

91
00:05:28,995 --> 00:05:30,495
a….

92
00:05:31,998 --> 00:05:35,001
My favorite onigiri shop kid.

93
00:05:35,001 --> 00:05:37,503
I'm a little in trouble.

94
00:05:37,503 --> 00:05:40,006
Ah, the speech shop.

95
00:05:40,006 --> 00:05:43,009
I know you well. I'm a big fan of CURO.

96
00:05:43,009 --> 00:05:46,509
Ah... So what kind of girl is the other person?

97
00:05:48,014 --> 00:05:50,516
I'm supposed to come and deliver it today.

98
00:05:50,516 --> 00:05:52,516
A gift?

99
00:05:55,521 --> 00:05:57,521
Excuse me.

100
00:06:07,467 --> 00:06:08,968
⚟Thank you for your hard work⚞

101
00:06:08,968 --> 00:06:11,971
Ah, thank you for your hard work...

102
00:06:11,971 --> 00:06:13,973
(Kiriya) Thank you, Shirase-san.

103
00:06:13,973 --> 00:06:15,975
No, you are welcome to order rice balls➡

104
00:06:15,975 --> 00:06:17,477
thank you.

105
00:06:17,477 --> 00:06:20,480
Kurosaki said he really wanted to do it.

106
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,982
Ah... could you please give it to me?

107
00:06:22,982 --> 00:06:24,984
Yes. I'll have one.

108
00:06:24,984 --> 00:06:26,984
No, it's okay. It's okay.

109
00:06:28,488 --> 00:06:29,989
(Kiriya) Excuse me, please bring it in➡

110
00:06:29,989 --> 00:06:32,492
Can I put it here?

111
00:06:32,492 --> 00:06:34,494
"amazing! 》

112
00:06:34,494 --> 00:06:37,494
《This is a movie shooting site! 》

113
00:06:38,498 --> 00:06:40,500
Mr. Shirase. Huh? Ah yes.

114
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:44,000
Could you please come here? yes.

115
00:06:45,505 --> 00:06:47,505
(Kiriya) Oh~｡

116
00:06:49,008 --> 00:06:52,011
If you have time, wait until Kurosaki's shooting is finished ➡

117
00:06:52,011 --> 00:06:54,514
Could you wait?

118
00:06:54,514 --> 00:06:58,017
Kurosaki was selfishly saying that he wanted to thank him directly.

119
00:06:58,017 --> 00:07:00,520
Ah... I'm fine though.

120
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:03,956
Where would you be...? If you are from there➡

121
00:07:03,956 --> 00:07:06,459
Please feel free to watch the filming.

122
00:07:06,459 --> 00:07:08,961
Eh, ah... then I'll do that.

123
00:07:08,961 --> 00:07:10,461
(Kiriya) Yes.

124
00:07:11,464 --> 00:07:13,466
⚟This is the line...⚞

125
00:07:13,466 --> 00:07:17,970
《Wow! He's a real actor~

126
00:07:17,970 --> 00:07:20,970
《I wanted to show it to Nacchan and the others~》

127
00:07:21,974 --> 00:07:24,477
⚟Cameras are rolling⚞ ⚟Cut 1 of scene 32! ⚞

128
00:07:24,477 --> 00:07:25,978
(clapperboard sound)

129
00:07:25,978 --> 00:07:28,478
(Yanagi) Okay, yes! (clapperboard sound)

130
00:07:32,485 --> 00:07:35,488
(Kazama) Thanks to you, I was saved.

131
00:07:35,488 --> 00:07:44,497
♬～

132
00:07:44,497 --> 00:07:47,500
《Mr. Kurosaki looks like an actor too》

133
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:51,000
Please don't worry...

134
00:07:53,005 --> 00:07:55,007
That... (Yanagi) Yes, cut!

135
00:07:55,007 --> 00:07:56,509
(clapperboard sound) ⚟Cut! ⚞

136
00:07:56,509 --> 00:07:58,511
Excuse me, can I ask you again?

137
00:07:58,511 --> 00:08:00,513
⚟Then let's go again⚞

138
00:08:00,513 --> 00:08:02,013
sorry.

139
00:08:06,953 --> 00:08:09,455
Cut 1 of 2. (clapperboard sound)

140
00:08:09,455 --> 00:08:12,455
(Yanagi) Okay, yes! (clapperboard sound)

141
00:08:18,965 --> 00:08:21,467
(Kazama) Thanks to you, I was saved.

142
00:08:21,467 --> 00:08:27,473
♬～

143
00:08:27,473 --> 00:08:30,977
No, please take care...

144
00:08:30,977 --> 00:08:32,478
(Yanagi) Yes, cut.

145
00:08:32,478 --> 00:08:34,480
⚟Cut! ⚞ (Clapperboard sound)

146
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:37,480
⚟Let's go again⚞ ⚟Yes, let's go again⚞

147
00:08:38,985 --> 00:08:40,987
《That's right》

148
00:08:40,987 --> 00:08:44,490
``Before, I hated attending award ceremonies.''

149
00:08:44,490 --> 00:08:47,493
《Kurosaki-san, you're working hard, aren't you?》

150
00:08:47,493 --> 00:08:49,495
(Yanagi) Let's calm down slowly.

151
00:08:49,495 --> 00:08:51,497
sorry….

152
00:08:51,497 --> 00:08:54,500
(Yanagi) Would you like to take a short break? Understood.

153
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:57,500
(Assistant Director) Sorry, everyone, please wait a moment.

154
00:09:13,953 --> 00:09:15,953
Mr. Kurosaki.

155
00:09:17,457 --> 00:09:19,459
Mr. Koharu.

156
00:09:19,459 --> 00:09:21,461
Thank you for coming.

157
00:09:21,461 --> 00:09:24,464
No, thank you very much.

158
00:09:24,464 --> 00:09:26,966
I was surprised when they brought me my rice balls!

159
00:09:26,966 --> 00:09:28,968
Dad looks like he's going to lose his temper!

160
00:09:28,968 --> 00:09:32,468
But today I put even more effort into making onigiri...

161
00:09:34,407 --> 00:09:36,909
I'm sorry but I can't speak fluently during this difficult time...

162
00:09:36,909 --> 00:09:39,412
Ah, no, I'm happy.

163
00:09:39,412 --> 00:09:41,912
I'll take it easy later.

164
00:09:44,917 --> 00:09:49,922
I thought I'd do my best if I could help...

165
00:09:49,922 --> 00:09:52,422
It's not going to be that easy.

166
00:09:53,926 --> 00:09:56,429
I thought I had prepared, but➡

167
00:09:56,429 --> 00:09:59,429
I never thought acting could be this difficult.

168
00:10:02,935 --> 00:10:06,435
"No, please don't worry."

169
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:11,444
"I guess I was waiting for you."

170
00:10:11,444 --> 00:10:15,444
"I guess I was waiting for you."

171
00:10:16,949 --> 00:10:18,451
please.

172
00:10:18,451 --> 00:10:20,953
Ah... what is this?

173
00:10:20,953 --> 00:10:23,456
This is a herbal tea to be delivered.

174
00:10:23,456 --> 00:10:25,958
My mother used to make this for me.

175
00:10:25,958 --> 00:10:28,961
I hope it makes you feel calmer.

176
00:10:28,961 --> 00:10:31,464
Herbal tea...

177
00:10:31,464 --> 00:10:46,913
♬～

178
00:10:46,913 --> 00:10:48,414
delicious.

179
00:10:48,414 --> 00:10:50,416
good.

180
00:10:50,416 --> 00:10:53,419
Actually, I've been nervous since this morning.

181
00:10:53,419 --> 00:10:55,421
I've been drinking this herbal tea.

182
00:10:55,421 --> 00:10:58,424
tension? Koharu-san, why?

183
00:10:58,424 --> 00:11:01,928
Why did you come to the filming site of “Hatsurai no Koi”➡

184
00:11:01,928 --> 00:11:04,931
It feels like a dream to bring my own rice balls.

185
00:11:04,931 --> 00:11:07,433
dream…?

186
00:11:07,433 --> 00:11:11,938
But in order to make Kurosaki's novel into a movie➡

187
00:11:11,938 --> 00:11:15,441
When I see so many people working hard➡

188
00:11:15,441 --> 00:11:17,941
This time I was impressed.

189
00:11:20,446 --> 00:11:23,950
Kurosaki-san’s desire to do his best➡

190
00:11:23,950 --> 00:11:29,455
I think this is clearly conveyed to everyone here.

191
00:11:29,455 --> 00:11:40,399
♬～

192
00:11:40,399 --> 00:11:42,902
Everyone is on Kurosaki-san's side.

193
00:11:42,902 --> 00:11:45,402
Of course me too.

194
00:11:46,405 --> 00:11:48,407
Koharu-san too...

195
00:11:48,407 --> 00:11:55,414
♬～

196
00:11:55,414 --> 00:11:58,417
Thank you, Koharu-san.

197
00:11:58,417 --> 00:11:59,917
yes.

198
00:12:03,422 --> 00:12:05,424
Yo, yes!

199
00:12:05,424 --> 00:12:06,924
(clapperboard sound)

200
00:12:12,431 --> 00:12:14,931
(Kazama) Thanks to you, I was saved.

201
00:12:18,938 --> 00:12:22,938
No, please don't worry.

202
00:12:26,445 --> 00:12:28,945
《Mr. Kurosaki is amazing! 》

203
00:12:32,451 --> 00:12:34,851
What are you writing in such a place?

204
00:12:35,888 --> 00:12:37,890
《Ah... that person! 》

205
00:12:37,890 --> 00:12:41,890
I guess I was waiting for you.

206
00:12:43,896 --> 00:12:47,896
Sorry for keeping you waiting.

207
00:12:49,402 --> 00:12:51,902
《She was an actress...》

208
00:12:54,407 --> 00:12:56,909
(Yanagi) Yes, OK! (clapperboard sound)

209
00:12:56,909 --> 00:12:58,911
⚟Yes, it's OK⚞ ⚟It's OK⚞

210
00:12:58,911 --> 00:13:00,911
⚟That was great⚞

211
00:13:02,415 --> 00:13:04,915
(Kazama) Thank you for your hard work. Thank you for your hard work.

212
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:09,922
Director, thank you for your help today.

213
00:13:09,922 --> 00:13:12,925
The teacher's performance was really good.

214
00:13:12,925 --> 00:13:15,925
Thank you very much. Thank you very much.

215
00:13:20,433 --> 00:13:21,934
(Arisugawa) CURO!

216
00:13:21,934 --> 00:13:24,437
That scene just now was so good!

217
00:13:24,437 --> 00:13:28,441
is that so? Acting so poorly in front of Mr. Arisugawa...

218
00:13:28,441 --> 00:13:30,443
It's embarrassing.

219
00:13:30,443 --> 00:13:32,445
Why are you so unsure?

220
00:13:32,445 --> 00:13:34,880
It was really wonderful.

221
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,880
I'm humbled.

222
00:13:39,385 --> 00:13:41,387
But thank you very much.

223
00:13:41,387 --> 00:13:43,389
(Hikaru) Don't you two look good together?

224
00:13:43,389 --> 00:13:46,392
(Wakana) A young genius writer and a movie actress.

225
00:13:46,392 --> 00:13:48,894
That's nice~

226
00:13:48,894 --> 00:13:53,399
(Hikaru) But isn't it surprising that CURO's gift is a rice ball?

227
00:13:53,399 --> 00:13:56,899
(Wakana) It's definitely too plain.

228
00:13:58,404 --> 00:14:02,408
(Arisugawa) I was really moved by how much soul there was in it.

229
00:14:02,408 --> 00:14:04,908
No, that's it...

230
00:14:06,412 --> 00:14:08,412
Let's have dinner together...

231
00:14:09,415 --> 00:14:11,417
Beat！

232
00:14:11,417 --> 00:14:15,421
Ah... Arisugawa-san, sorry, I'm here.

233
00:14:15,421 --> 00:14:19,421
picture? Eh... oh wait!

234
00:14:23,429 --> 00:14:28,434
《I... I wonder why I was so excited》

235
00:14:28,434 --> 00:14:32,438
Mr. Koharu, sorry to have kept you waiting, do you still have any left?

236
00:14:32,438 --> 00:14:33,873
yes.

237
00:14:40,379 --> 00:14:42,379
Mr. Koharu?

238
00:14:47,386 --> 00:14:51,891
Mr. Kurosaki... he's definitely an amazing person.

239
00:14:51,891 --> 00:14:53,891
Is it me?

240
00:14:55,895 --> 00:14:58,395
The novel is amazing too...

241
00:15:00,399 --> 00:15:03,399
The play was also really great.

242
00:15:09,909 --> 00:15:14,914
Koharu-san is more amazing than me, right?

243
00:15:14,914 --> 00:15:16,916
picture?

244
00:15:16,916 --> 00:15:20,920
If I was the person I used to be, I wouldn't want to appear in a movie➡

245
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:25,424
I refused because I was afraid of failing.

246
00:15:25,424 --> 00:15:28,928
But at the award ceremony➡

247
00:15:28,928 --> 00:15:31,931
Koharu-san said that, right?

248
00:15:31,931 --> 00:15:35,331
Don't be disappointed if I fail.

249
00:15:37,370 --> 00:15:43,376
Since then, Koharu-san’s words have made me smile➡

250
00:15:43,376 --> 00:15:46,379
It gives me courage.

251
00:15:46,379 --> 00:15:48,381
Mr. Kurosaki...

252
00:15:48,381 --> 00:15:57,890
♬～

253
00:15:57,890 --> 00:16:01,894
Koharu-san is my goddess.

254
00:16:01,894 --> 00:16:03,896
Oh... I can't believe she's a goddess.

255
00:16:03,896 --> 00:16:08,901
I feel like I can do anything if Koharu-san is here.

256
00:16:08,901 --> 00:16:12,905
I'm sure you can fly even in the sky.

257
00:16:12,905 --> 00:16:15,408
Fufufu…!

258
00:16:15,408 --> 00:16:19,412
Koharu-san's rice balls are my best reward today.

259
00:16:19,412 --> 00:16:21,414
I'll enjoy having this.

260
00:16:21,414 --> 00:16:22,914
yes.

261
00:16:25,418 --> 00:16:28,421
(Sound of taking rice balls)

262
00:16:28,421 --> 00:16:31,921
(sound of peeling off film)

263
00:16:33,426 --> 00:16:36,862
《I had leftover rice balls➡

264
00:16:36,862 --> 00:16:42,868
But I'll be happy if I can be of help to Kurosaki-san.

265
00:16:42,868 --> 00:16:45,371
(Yanagi) Is this the rice ball you mentioned?

266
00:16:45,371 --> 00:16:47,371
Supervisor Liu.

267
00:16:50,876 --> 00:16:52,878
(Yanagi) Oh~｡

268
00:16:52,878 --> 00:16:56,382
This is packed with love, nutrition and deliciousness➡

269
00:16:56,382 --> 00:16:58,884
This is the best rice ball Shirase rice ball.

270
00:16:58,884 --> 00:17:01,887
Please feel free to have as many as you want.

271
00:17:01,887 --> 00:17:04,387
Ah, this is it.

272
00:17:05,891 --> 00:17:08,394
Well then, I'll have it.

273
00:17:08,394 --> 00:17:15,901
♬～

274
00:17:15,901 --> 00:17:18,901
Yes, it's delicious!

275
00:17:20,906 --> 00:17:23,409
It tastes so good!

276
00:17:23,409 --> 00:17:25,411
Ah... I'm honored!

277
00:17:25,411 --> 00:17:26,912
(Yanagi) Delicious!

278
00:17:26,912 --> 00:17:28,912
Everyone please!

279
00:17:30,416 --> 00:17:31,916
please!

280
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:35,921
yes.

281
00:17:35,921 --> 00:17:45,931
♬～

282
00:17:45,931 --> 00:17:48,934
Did you eat it? Please eat.Please eat.

283
00:17:48,934 --> 00:17:50,936
⚟The rice is delicious! ⚞

284
00:17:50,936 --> 00:17:53,939
Yes, please tell the location valve.

285
00:17:53,939 --> 00:17:56,942
Please let me know!

286
00:17:56,942 --> 00:18:07,942
♬～

287
00:18:10,956 --> 00:18:12,456
Okay...｡

288
00:18:15,961 --> 00:18:17,963
(Arisugawa) Mr. Koharu.

289
00:18:17,963 --> 00:18:19,463
picture?

290
00:18:21,467 --> 00:18:23,467
Is it okay?

291
00:18:24,970 --> 00:18:28,474
Um... Mr. Arisugawa?

292
00:18:28,474 --> 00:18:31,474
why my name?

293
00:18:32,978 --> 00:18:37,483
Can you... please stop clinging to CURO anymore?

294
00:18:37,483 --> 00:18:38,983
picture?

295
00:18:40,486 --> 00:18:44,490
CURO and you live in different worlds.

296
00:18:44,490 --> 00:18:48,994
You know that you and him are not a match, right?

297
00:18:48,994 --> 00:18:50,996
《What is it? This person》

298
00:18:50,996 --> 00:18:53,932
《Why did this happen all of a sudden...》

299
00:18:53,932 --> 00:18:57,436
Just now, I held your hand in a public place.

300
00:18:57,436 --> 00:18:59,938
What would you do if someone saw you?

301
00:18:59,938 --> 00:19:01,440
Scandal in one➡

302
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:03,942
This movie might fly!?

303
00:19:03,942 --> 00:19:06,942
That... that's...

304
00:19:07,946 --> 00:19:11,946
It seems like no one will tell you, so I'll tell you.

305
00:19:13,452 --> 00:19:15,952
You're in the way.

306
00:19:17,456 --> 00:19:19,958
Stay away from CURO.

307
00:19:19,958 --> 00:19:32,471
♬～

308
00:19:32,471 --> 00:19:35,974
《Certainly... Me and Kurosaki-san➡

309
00:19:35,974 --> 00:19:39,478
Maybe the world we live in is different.

310
00:19:39,478 --> 00:19:51,490
♬～

311
00:19:51,490 --> 00:19:55,928
《But... still》

312
00:19:55,928 --> 00:20:00,928
I hate that I won't be able to see Kurosaki-san anymore!

313
00:20:02,434 --> 00:20:05,938
Hehe... Ahaha!

314
00:20:05,938 --> 00:20:10,943
If so...I'll take it away.

315
00:20:10,943 --> 00:20:12,943
Take it away?

316
00:20:16,448 --> 00:20:19,952
I'm sure you'll regret it.

317
00:20:19,952 --> 00:20:28,961
♬～

318
00:20:28,961 --> 00:20:31,961
Thank you very much. We look forward to seeing you again.

319
00:20:39,972 --> 00:20:43,976
``I said something like that, but is it okay? 》

320
00:20:43,976 --> 00:20:45,978
(Chifuyu) Sister?

321
00:20:45,978 --> 00:20:47,980
Ah, welcome back.

322
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:49,982
(Chifuyu) I'm home.

323
00:20:49,982 --> 00:20:52,918
(Natsuki) Hey, how are you doing?

324
00:20:52,918 --> 00:20:54,318
Huh?

325
00:20:56,922 --> 00:20:58,924
Nacchan?

326
00:20:58,924 --> 00:21:01,424
Hey, cheer up.

327
00:21:05,931 --> 00:21:08,934
《I can't believe I'm worrying both Chi-chan and Nacchan➡

328
00:21:08,934 --> 00:21:11,934
I have to be strong》

329
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:18,443
Thank you, I'm feeling better!

330
00:21:18,443 --> 00:21:20,445
(Natsuki) Really? Yeah.

331
00:21:20,445 --> 00:21:22,948
I'll make you a big hamburger tonight as a thank you!

332
00:21:22,948 --> 00:21:24,950
Yay!

333
00:21:24,950 --> 00:21:28,453
Well, I'll be going home first. Yes, thank you.

334
00:21:28,453 --> 00:21:35,961
♬～

335
00:21:35,961 --> 00:21:39,961
``Don't let things like this make you weak! 》

336
00:21:44,970 --> 00:21:46,471
Koharu-chan

337
00:21:46,471 --> 00:21:48,473
Ah, Yuio-san, thank you for your hard work.

338
00:21:48,473 --> 00:21:51,476
Thank you for your continued support today.

339
00:21:51,476 --> 00:21:54,876
Ah, that's right, Koharu-chan, do you know this?

340
00:21:59,918 --> 00:22:01,418
picture…?

341
00:22:02,921 --> 00:22:06,425
Is this Mr. Kurosaki and Mr. Arisugawa?

342
00:22:06,425 --> 00:22:09,428
This has become a rumor among fans.

343
00:22:09,428 --> 00:22:13,932
Then Rei Arisugawa updated her Minster.

344
00:22:13,932 --> 00:22:21,940
♬～

345
00:22:21,940 --> 00:22:26,445
♬～

346
00:22:26,445 --> 00:22:29,448
There are rumors that the two are lovers➡

347
00:22:29,448 --> 00:22:31,450
Is it true?

348
00:22:31,450 --> 00:22:33,450
lover?

349
00:22:34,953 --> 00:22:39,453
These two look great together.
